  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb2\u0b95 \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b95\u0baf\u0bc0\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Pudukudiripu Division Divisional Secretariat Officers Health Leave Strike",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Pudukudiripu Divisional Secretariat staff on Monday 01st Sukaina said that taking the minimum amount of fuel that was kept safe for essential purposes from Mullaitivu Pudukudiripu Divisional Secretariat and posting on social networking sites that the police and some regional youths have seized ganja or drugs is not only unnecessary but also a planned act of humiliation to our divisional secretariat and officials. They are engaged in a leave strike.",
        "In this way, the employees of the Divisional Secretariat, who are involved in the health leave protest, commented,",
        "In this time of economic crisis, there are more power cuts, so it is not a big crime to buy 50 liters of diesel in advance for the needs of the generator.",
        "Since the storage room is prone to rats and the bathroom is the least heated area, it is normal to store fuel in the bathroom, but this is not fuel hoarding. In any case keeping a minimum quantity of oil for the use of a kerosene water-cooling machine can be considered an offence.",
        "All these fuels are found in minimum quantity in our Divisional Secretariat for essential needs.",
        "Therefore, considering only the speech of a few people, which is not fair in any way, the said action taken by the officer in charge of Pudukudiripu Police Station has caused mental distress to the Divisional Secretary and all the divisional secretariat officers, in order to protest against the said action, we would like to inform you that on Monday 01st, all the officers will be participating in the healthy leave protest.",
        "It is noteworthy that Pudukudiripu Divisional Secretariat and Divisional Secretary's residence were raided by Pudukudiripu police and some regional youths on the night of 30th and a small amount of fuel was recovered."
      ],
